<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="{{@site.locale}}">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Square 101 | {{@site.title}}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{asset "css/style.css"}}">
    
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="{{asset "icons/squareone.ico"}}">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" type="image/x-icon" href="{{asset "icons/squareone.ico"}}">

    <link rel="me" href="https://social.lol/@amit" />
    <link rel="me" href="https://github.com/am1t">
    <link rel="me" href="https://micro.blog/amit" />
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="square-card">
            <img src="{{asset "images/squareone.png"}}" alt="Square 101 Icon" class="square-icon">
            
            <h1 class="square-heading"><a href="{{@site.url}}">Square 101</a></h1>
            <div class="square-subheading">Kickstarting Curiosity, One Topic at a Time.</div>
            
            <div class="square-intro">
                <p>A short, sharp introduction (<strong>101</strong>) to words you hear often — but no one ever explains. Delivered on <strong>1st & 15th</strong> of every month in 500 words.
                    A perfect way to fill in the gaps, <span style="font-style: italic;">without it feeling like homework.</span>
                </p>
                <p>You can read more about the newsletter <a href="{{@site.url}}/blog/introducing-square-101">here on my blog</a>.</p>
            </div>
            
            <iframe id="beehiiv-iframe" src="https://embeds.beehiiv.com/e989db60-b6d7-4761-9cab-c23828e29e9a?slim=true" 
                data-test-id="beehiiv-embed" 
                height="52" 
                frameborder="0" 
                scrolling="no" style="margin: 0; border-radius: 0px !important; background-color: transparent;border-radius: 10px;margin: 2rem auto 0 auto;width: 100%;">
            </iframe>
            <div id="form-footer" class="form-footer">
                No spam. No hype. Just clarity. You can unsubscribe at any time.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            const iframe = document.getElementById('beehiiv-iframe');
            const footer = document.getElementById('form-footer');
            
            // Show footer after iframe loads
            iframe.addEventListener('load', function() {
                footer.classList.add('visible');
            });
            
            // Fallback in case iframe load event doesn't fire
            setTimeout(function() {
                footer.classList.add('visible');
            }, 10000);
        });
        </script>

        {{#get "posts" filter="tag:101" include="tags,authors" limit="20" order="published_at desc"}}
            {{#if posts}}
                <h2 style="color:#f9bf77 !important;text-align: center; margin: 5rem 0 0px; color: var(--text);">Previous Issues </h2>
                <p style="color:#ddd !important;text-align: center; margin: 1rem 0 1rem; color: var(--text);">
                    The newsletter is powered by <a href="https://beehiiv.com">beehiiv</a> — you can subscribe for free above, and cancel anytime. You can find the archive down below.
                </p>
            {{/if}}
        {{/get}}
        
        <div class="post-cards">
            {{#get "posts" filter="tag:101" include="tags,authors" limit="20" order="published_at desc"}}
                {{#foreach posts}}
                    <a href="{{url}}" class="post-card">
                        <div class="post-card-title">{{title}}</div>
                        <div class="post-card-date">{{date format="M Y"}}</div>
                        <div class="post-card-summary">{{excerpt words="20"}}</div>
                    </a>
                {{/foreach}}
            {{/get}}
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="fade"></div>
    <footer>
        <nav class="nav">
            <div class="links">
                <a href="{{@site.url}}"><img src="{{asset "icons/home.svg"}}" width="24" height="24" alt="Home" target="_blank"/></a>
                <a href="https://www.buymeacoffee.com/amitgawande"><img src="{{asset "icons/buymeacoffee.svg"}}" width="24" height="24" alt="Buy Me A Coffee"/></a>
                <a href="{{@site.url}}/rss/"><img src="{{asset "icons/rss.svg"}}" width="24" height="24" alt="RSS" target="_blank"/></a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </footer>
</body>
</html> 